<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Shelter Match</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        /* Banner section */
        .banner {
            background-image: url('/img/page/banner.jpg'); /* Replace with your image path */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 25vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        .banner::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Dark overlay for text readability */
        }
        .banner-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            display: block;
            margin-right: -45%;
        }
        .banner h2 {
            font-size: .8em;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: -25px;
            margin-left: -140px;
        }
        .banner h1 {
            font-size: 3.2em;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        /* Not banner */
        .mission {
            font-size: 1em;
            margin: 0 auto;
            margin-top: 30px;
            max-width: 60%;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
        }
        .find-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #A2BA77;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 40px;
        }
        .demo-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }
        #demo {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Banner Section -->
    <div class="banner">
        <div class="banner-content">
            <h2>Animals Need</h2>
            <h1>Your Help!</h1>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Remaining Section -->
    <p class="mission">
        Our mission is to help you find the perfect next member of your family. Luckily, we know lots of fun and loving pets looking for a home. Shelter Match works with a variety of shelters to help match shelter animals with loving homes. Use our main page to see pets that canâ€™t wait to meet you. When you find the perfect fit, reach out to the shelter listed on the right side to set up a visit. Select the button below to get started!
    </p>
    <p></p>
    <p class="mission">
        For our nonprofit and animal shelter partners, please use the Pets section in the top right to add any pets that still need a home and remove any that have been placed.
    </p>

    <div class="demo-container">
    <img id='demo' src="/img/page/demo.jpg">
</div>

    <a href="/index" class="find-button">Find A Pet Now</a>

</body>
</html>